race.comment: BLACKLIST (3) has performed well in two runs since transferring to the Mack Griffith stable. Went to Eagle Farm last start where he overcame a slow start to be beaten under a length in a Class 3 over 1805m. Nicely in after Nock's claim and will get all the favours from the inside stall. HAWK POWER (1) raced handy but his condition gave out when resuming over 1890m at Newcastle last time out in what has turned out to be a strong form race. Will take a lot from that testing first-up assignment and is a serious threat. Greybeard CHATEAUX PARK (8) turned back the clock with a barnstorming win over 1900m at Newcastle recently. Up in class but cannot be overlooked down on the limit. MAGIC PHAROAH (9) hasn't won for a while but is capable of sneaking into the top four.
